profile:
Welcome to Budget Blinds of Thunder Bay. We have been servicing Thunder bay for over 12 years for all of their custom window covering needs. We are your local experts and are proud to be backed by the #1 provider of custom window coverings in North America. Budget Blinds has provided design-driven solutions for over 25 years. With the highest levels of customer satisfaction, you'll have the peace of mind and security that comes with choosing the proven leader. We’ll get to know you and your unique style so we can deliver the perfect solution for your home. On top of all that we carry a 5 year, no questions asked, limited warranty on all custom window coverings.  

***

Explore what Beautiful can do for your windows. Contact us today to schedule your appointment. We’re looking forward to working with you.
products: Custom blinds, Shades, Shutters, Drapery, hardware and more.
services: In home consultation, expert measuring, professional installation, repairs and warranty assistance.
brands: Enlightened Styles, Signature Series, Mera, Horizons, Elite, Lantex, Lutron, Maxmar, Normans, Phase II, Inspired Shades, Shadomatic, Somfy, Thomas Hicks, Vadain
specialities: Motorization, exterior / interior shades, enclosed blinds, shutters, faux wood, real wood, sustainable materials for shades, shutters and  temperature regulating window solutions. Able to cover tricky angled windows, skylights,  and round windows. Window film also available.
warranty_terms: 5 year, no questions asked, limited warranty
